# Christian Garcia

## Engineering Scientist Associate Cloud & Interactive Computing

Email: **[cgarcia@tacc.utexas.edu](mailto:cgarcia@tacc.utexas.edu)**

Christian began working part-time at TACC with an REU internship in January 2019 after taking TACC led classes as a Computational Engineering student at UT. He continued with TACC after graduation with a professional internship starting in December 2019. He transitioned to full-time staff in June 2020 and is currently working in CIC on various Tapis services.

### Current Projects

* Tapis Pods Service
* PgREST
* Abaco
* Tapipy
* Tapis Service

### Education

**B.S., Computational Engineering**  

The University of Texas at Austin